{"type": "article", "id": 34676, "title": "范思哲酒店在迪拜开业，以及，蕾哈娜和PUMA合作发布天鹅绒款球鞋 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2016-11-21T02:31:46Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 2809, "name": "周边"}, {"id": 9968, "name": "手机壳"}, {"id": 1231, "name": "PUMA"}, {"id": 2710, "name": "A&F"}, {"id": 2910, "name": "Hugo Boss"}, {"id": 6542, "name": "范思哲"}, {"id": 14669, "name": "Chiara Ferragni"}, {"id": 35032, "name": "仓石一树"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 37, "image": "img/article/article_show/20161121075353sYMXkTqc5xtWAaJo.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.vogue.co.uk/article/hugo-boss-womenswear-not-showing-new-york-fashion-week\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Hugo Boss 将不会参加明年二月的纽约时装周</b></a> | Hugo Boss 近日宣布，由 Jason Wu 带领的女装支线，将不会参加明年二月的纽约时装周。此举是 Hugo Boss 品牌重塑，要专注做男装的一部分。Hugo Boss 表示，将在 2018 年之前完成公司策略的转变。<br></p><p><a href=\"https://www.luxurydaily.com/versace-branded-resorts-enter-middle-east-with-dubai-opening/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Palazzo Versace 在迪拜开业</b></a> | Versace 集团旗下的高端五星级酒店 Palazzo Versace 在迪拜开业，宣布由此进入中东高端旅游消费市场。整个酒店包含 215 个房间，室内设计出自 Versace 的创意总监 Donatella Versace 之手。</p><p><a href=\"http://www.marketwatch.com/story/abercrombie-fitch-is-trying-to-rebrand-but-its-actually-just-confusing-customers-2016-11-18\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>A&amp;F 第三季度营收下跌 14% </b></a>| Abercrombie &amp; Fitch 曾在去年八月更换过设计团队，想要通过提供不再性感的衣服，来覆盖更多的市场。不过，此举似乎并未奏效。A&amp;F 最新的财报显示，该集团第三季度营收下跌了 14%，为 8.217 亿美元。&nbsp;</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>由日本设计师仓石一树创立的概念精选店 heather grey wall，曾在 2013 年在上海开过期间限定 pop up 店。<a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/11/heather-grey-wall-shanghai-opening-2\" rel=\"nofollow\">日前，heather grey wall 正式入驻上海徐汇区华亭路的一栋四层洋房之中</a>，开业当天吸引众多潮流大咖到场，包括陈冠希和<a href=\"http://honeyee.com\" rel=\"nofollow\"> </a>honeyee.com 主编铃木哲、Jam Home Made 主理人增井元纪等人物。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161121075629medByiok5alnWqu8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161121075631ezPEUYSjTBRNVfct.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667236\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161121075631Yj4yTpEvaC5UczKF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161121075631EqAezPBJ7DTRf8ks.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161121075633Sq914FZoUsKfwiBH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161121075633IQRvyTuZe9rPktpn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667806\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161121075646Xzu6OeRmCHNfh0ns.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161121075646J5fOYjkNwim0ghZC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161121075647u3IyUJfkNanmh6tq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667806\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"http://www.kidulty.com/news/detail/id/4040/ak/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Rihanna 携 2016 年度最佳球鞋 Fenty PUMA Creeper 回归</a>，发布全新配色系列。该系列以意大利手工制作，鞋身采用了奢华的天鹅绒，加以烫金 logo，共有灰、红、黑三色可供选择，将于 12 月 8 日正式发售。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161121075659fPWrHc3qoZRAvSJT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161121075721PVgeL3DRrpQ19bJH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161121075721M4JQxWzEglIXBSCi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161121075721IOVn4YHPLREiA0mM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://popbee.com/lifestyle/movies/fantastic-beasts-wands/#\" rel=\"nofollow\">《神奇动物在哪里》官方推出四款巫师手杖</a>，还原度还挺高的。这四支手杖定价均为 49.99 美元，将于 11 月 30 日正式推出。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161121075731IMv5OGYxh8JXNLVC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">即将迎来创办 20 周年之际，<a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/11/mastermind-japan-iphone-7-cases-apple-watch-straps\" rel=\"nofollow\">mastermind JAPAN 发布 Pre-20th 特别系列</a>。该系列包括一组 iPhone case 和 Apple watch 表带，目前已于伊势丹开放预购，预计 12 月底到明年 1 月上旬正式发售。&nbsp;<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161121075745RuboEMFpnhCaXqsy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161121075758CHG3qZybcY8wPpxr.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498000\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161121075815ULyV3z6lqrwoHKdN.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.502000\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161121075816sHXSVfZK8BEQ2Mmw.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">于 2012 创立的中性街头品牌 <a href=\"http://www.severenature.com/collection\" rel=\"nofollow\">severe nature</a> ， 发布了 2016 秋冬季全新系列 origins。该系列以暗黑为主调，加入了法兰绒、拼贴、刺绣等元素，售价从 59.99 至 99.99 美元不等。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161121075828e3257OyqvDHg9PBm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161121075828ubOI1oyZlPfTe5NW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161121075828LcSmvkyGJ1do9UlP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161121075829zCt3B9J0s1pVciSr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611210758290Ehq7anSZvk1JKbm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161121075829xIi1CbmyOrnHhRMV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161121075836g4L0XTKoWEJvw2rF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611210758368uS7VAljmWqZBC5f.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>上周六，<a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/retail/chiara-ferragni-first-u-s-pop-up-to-open-at-the-grove-10709286/\" rel=\"nofollow\">时尚博主 Chiara Ferragni 在洛杉矶开了美国第一家独立期间限定店铺</a>。 Chiara Ferragni 早早地涉足时尚设计圈，美国轻奢网站  The Blonde Salad 拥有 Ferragni 鞋履系列的授权，不过，独立出店这还是第一次。这家店铺占地 200 平方英尺，整体装修上以银色为主调，出售 Ferragni 的秋冬系列商品。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161121101532phZjkFBQ5fDdTIiW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563272\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161121101540PEbFM9fBjlrkDvqK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.708008\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}